    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs required level 3) is acknowledged and accepted on the basis that ASTM F1717 specifies a single standard configuration and regulatory precedent supports this limitation. All QoI comparisons satisfy pre-established acceptance bounds (E/uval < 1.96; relative error < 10%). Overall credibility is sufficient for a Medium model risk, Medium decision consequence context of use.",
